#

this directory contains R sources

lx          : basic R utilities package
xlx         : lx extensions for genomics
asdog       : CNV analysis package
rbgzf       : bgzf bindings
thmm        : tiny HMM package

packages    : thirdparty R packages used in WGInR
              please use CRAN version, whenever possible
              these packages are included just in case of trouble
              with newer or unsupported packages

etc         : some internal scripts used in Makefile

scripts     : asdog and other scripts (will be copied into ../scripts upon install)

tests       : some tests (unfinished)

to compile and install :

$ make all install

in case of trouble when compiling please read: 
  ../../docs/Readme_RPackages.txt
  ../../README
